OL,6,FPaula Vennells "slavishly" maintained
OL,7,Fthe Horizon system was robust despite
OL,8,Fbeing aware of its faults, her former
OL,9,FRoyal Mail Group counterpart has said.
OL,11,FDame Moya Greene told the Horizon IT
OL,12,Finquiry she initially backed Venells
OL,13,Fas the crisis began but changed her
OL,14,Fstance after seeing evidence emerge
OL,15,Ffrom the inquiry which led her to
OL,16,Fbelieve the former Post Office chief
OL,17,Fexecutive knew about Horizon's faults.
