OL,4,CHorizon was fine despite knowing faults
OL,6,FIn an exchange of messages before she
OL,7,Faccused Ms Vennells of knowing about
OL,8,Fthe system errors, Dame Moya told her:
OL,9,F"What a terrible time. Just tell the
OL,10,Ftruth.
OL,12,F"I know you are a good person and
OL,13,Ffriends will be hard to find now."What
OL,14,Fhas happened is a terrible... horrible
OL,15,Fthing.
OL,17,F"So many lives ruined. Yours too."
