OL,6,FShe later told Ms Vennells, in an
OL,7,Fexchange previously shown to the
OL,8,Finquiry during the former Post Office
OL,9,Fboss's evidence: "When it was clear
OL,10,Fthe system was at fault, the PO should
OL,11,Fhave raised a red flag, stopped all
OL,12,Fproceedings, given people back their
OL,13,Fmoney and then tried to compensate
OL,14,Fthem for the ruin this caused in their
OL,15,Flives."
OL,17,FAfter Ms Vennells agreed the toll on
OL,18,Feveryone had been "dreadful", Dame
OL,19,FMoya added: "I don't know what to say.
OL,20,FI think you knew."
