OL,6,FMore than 700 subpostmasters were
OL,7,Fprosecuted by the Post Office and
OL,8,Fhanded criminal convictions between
OL,9,F1999 and 2015 as Fujitsu's faulty
OL,10,FHorizon system made it appear as
OL,11,Fthough money was missing at their
OL,12,Fbranches.
OL,14,FHundreds of victims are awaiting
OL,15,Fcompensation despite the previous
OL,16,Fgovernment announcing that those who
OL,17,Fhave had convictions quashed are
OL,18,Feligible for #600,000 payouts.
